Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,无法赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,根本无法赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,原来他们是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,根本无法赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们当初说好了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等知道了一切之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你就会杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,时候已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,来，你动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快动手
